# Design Brief

Ingest moodboard images, brand assets, and style references from the change path. Combine with market analysis findings to produce a design brief with concrete design tokens, typography, color palette, and visual direction.

<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>
You MUST write output to: {{task.changePath}}/design-brief.md

This step produces a design brief. Do NOT write copy, create code, or build anything.
</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>

## Process

```dot
digraph brief {
    rankdir=TB;
    read [label="Read all files\nin change path" shape=box];
